object.script:
-- -> 0deg V90deg <180deg ^270deg tyaw = 0 yawup = 1 targets = {} srans = {45,60,90,180} mode = 3 sran = srans[mode] touched = false
zoom = {5000,2500,1000,500,100,50} zoomMode = 0 clicked = false
found = {}
function onTick() inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) tdis = input.getNumber(7) --sran = input.getNumber(8) --45d, 90d, 180d sspd = input.getNumber(8) --scanspeed tdet = input.getBool(3) --target detected revs = input.getBool(4) --downward?
if (math.abs(tyaw)>sran) and (sran~=180) then yawup = yawup*-1 end tyaw = tyaw + yawup*sspd/5 if tyaw>=180 then tyaw = -180 end
for i,v in ipairs(found) do v[3] = v[3]-1 if v[3]<0 then table.remove(found,i) end end
if tdet then table.insert(found, {tyaw, tdis, 255}) end
isPressingRectangle = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 0, 26, 9, 10)
if isPressingRectangle then clicked = true end
if not isPressed then if clicked then zoomMode = (zoomMode+1)%#zoom clicked = false elseif touched then mode = (mode+1)%#srans yawup = 1 tyaw = 0 found = nil found = {} end end touched = isPressed sran = srans[mode+1]
if revs then output.setNumber(1, -tyaw/360) else output.setNumber(1, tyaw/360) end output.setNumber(2, radius) output.setNumber(3, centerH) end
function drawPixel(x, y) screen.drawText(x-1, y-4, ".") end
function drawArcDash(x, y, r, st, w) for i=st, (st+w)-1 do x1, y1 = x + r*math.cos(math.rad(i)), y + r*math.sin(math.rad(i)) drawPixel(x1,y1) end end
function drawBackground(x, y, r, st, w) local k = math.floor(math.log(r)) for i=1, k do drawArcDash(x, y, r*i/k, st, w) end if sran ~= 180 then x1, y1 = x + r*math.cos(math.rad(st)), y + r*math.sin(math.rad(st)) screen.drawLine(x, y, x1, y1) x1, y1 = x + r*math.cos(math.rad(st+w)), y + r*math.sin(math.rad(st+w)) screen.drawLine(x, y, x1, y1) end end
function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() screenH, screenW = screen.getHeight(), screen.getWidth() screen.setColor(0,32,0)
if sran ~= 180 then radius = screenW/(2*math.sin(math.rad(sran)))*0.9 else radius = screenH/2*0.9 end centerH = screenH/2 + screenH*(180-sran)/300
drawBackground(screenW/2, centerH, radius, 270-sran, 2*sran)
x3, y3 = screenW/2 + radius*math.cos(math.rad(tyaw-90)), centerH + radius*math.sin(math.rad(tyaw-90)) screen.drawLine(screenW/2, centerH, x3, y3)
--screen.drawText(0,0,screenW.."x"..screenH) --screen.drawText(0, 0, sran*2) screen.drawTextBox(0, 0, screenW, screenH, zoom[zoomMode+1], 1, -1)
for i, v in ipairs(found) do screen.setColor(255, 0, 0, v[3]) xt, yt = screenW/2 + radius*v[2]/zoom[zoomMode+1]*math.cos(math.rad(v[1]-90)), centerH + radius*v[2]/zoom[zoomMode+1]*math.sin(math.rad(v[1]-90)) drawPixel(xt, yt) end
screen.setColor(0, 255, 0)
end

object.script:
function onTick() PitchI = input.getNumber(1) RollI = input.getNumber(2) VS = input.getNumber(3) HSI = input.getNumber(4) SSI = input.getNumber(5)
OFS = input.getNumber(10) PF = input.getNumber(11) RF = input.getNumber(12)
AltModeI = input.getBool(21) Alt = input.getNumber(22) Fuel = input.getNumber(23) HdgI = input.getNumber(24)
if AltModeI then AltMode = "B" else AltMode = "R" end
SS=SSI*math.cos(math.pi*RollI*2)
HS = HSI- SS if HS == 0 then HS = 0.001 end
Pitch = PitchI*PF Roll = RollI*RF
if HdgI <=0 then Hdg = HdgI*-360 elseif HdgI >0 then Hdg = (1-HdgI)*360 end end
function onDraw()
w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(0,255,0,100) for i=-10,10,1 do screen.drawLine(20, h/2+5*h/2*(Pitch+0.0278*i)-OFS,30,h/2+5*h/2*(Pitch+0.0278*i)-OFS) end
screen.setColor(0,255,0,255) screen.drawTextBox(0, 0, w-2, 9, math.floor(HS*10+0,5)/10, 1, -1) screen.drawTextBox(0, 7, w-2, 9, math.floor(Alt+0.5)..""..AltMode, 1, -1) if Fuel <= 300 then screen.setColor(255,0,0,255) end screen.drawTextBox(0, 14, w-2, 9, math.floor(Fuel+0.5), 1, -1) screen.setColor(0,255,0,255) screen.drawTextBox(0, 21, w-2, 9, math.floor(Hdg), 1, -1)
for i=-50,410,10 do screen.setColor(0,255,0,100) screen.drawLine(w/2+i-Hdg,h,w/2+i-Hdg,h-5)
screen.setColor(0,255,0) if i==0 or i ==360 then screen.drawTextBox(w/2+i-Hdg-4, h-15, 9, 10, "N", 0, 1) end if i==90 then screen.drawTextBox(w/2+i-Hdg-4, h-15, 9, 10, "E", 0, 1) end if i==180 then screen.drawTextBox(w/2+i-Hdg-4, h-15, 9, 10, "S", 0, 1) end if i==270 then screen.drawTextBox(w/2+i-Hdg-4, h-15, 9, 10, "W", 0, 1) end end
screen.setColor(0,255,0,155) screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2+5*h/2*Pitch-OFS, w-20, h/2+5*h/2*Pitch-math.sin(math.pi*Roll*2)*h/2-OFS) screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2+5*h/2*Pitch-OFS, 20, h/2+5*h/2*Pitch+math.sin(math.pi*Roll*2)*h/2-OFS)
if VS < 0 then screen.setColor(255,0,0,255) else screen.setColor(0,255,0,255) end screen.drawLine(w-5, h/2-OFS, w-5, h/2-VS*2-OFS)
screen.setColor(55,255,55,255) screen.drawLine(w/2-10,h/2-OFS,w/2-5,h/2-OFS) screen.drawLine(w/2+10,h/2-OFS,w/2+5,h/2-OFS) screen.drawLine(w/2,h/2-5-OFS,w/2,h/2-10-OFS)
screen.setColor(0,155,0,255)
screen.drawCircle(w/2+SS*2, h/2-VS-OFS, 2)
screen.drawLine(w/2+SS*2-5*math.cos(math.pi*Roll*2),h/2-VS+math.sin(math.pi*Roll*2)*5-OFS,w/2+SS*2-2*math.cos(math.pi*Roll*2),h/2-VS+math.sin(math.pi*Roll*2)*2-OFS)
screen.drawLine(w/2+SS*2+5*math.cos(math.pi*Roll*2),h/2-VS-math.sin(math.pi*Roll*2)*5-OFS,w/2+SS*2+2*math.cos(math.pi*Roll*2),h/2-VS-math.sin(math.pi*Roll*2)*2-OFS)
end
